          <avActivityHighlights>Low avalanche danger will prevail. In the regions exposed to heavier precipitation the avalanche prone locations are more prevalent.</avActivityHighlights>
          <avActivityComment>The wind slabs are bonding poorly with the old snowpack in particular on steep shady slopes. The avalanche prone locations are to be found in particular adjacent to ridgelines and in gullies and bowls and at transitions from a shallow to a deep snowpack.</avActivityComment>
